-- Blockbuster buys movie download service Movielink
-- 
-- Wed Aug 8, 2007 7:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/08/us-blockbuster-movielink-idUSWEN028820070808

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Blockbuster Inc BBI.N, the No. 1 U.S. movie rental chain, said on Wednesday it has acquired movie download service Movielink for undisclosed terms. 

 Blockbuster has been in talks to purchase Movielink since at least March. At that time, sources familiar with the situation said the purchase price was under $50 million in cash and stock. (Reporting by  Gina Keating )